details.name: Street Race - The Business End
details.creator: RSI_sidhant
details.desc: Pay cuts, lack of safety equipment, Taco Bomb Tuesdays abolished, and now street racers juiced on cans of Junk are cutting through the construction site. These contractors are just one failed handbrake turn away from federal investigation and becoming a legend of the San Andreas racing circuit. Lap race for Los Santos Tuners.
